# exec-python

Minimal engine to execute python code generated by LLMs, with a lot of customisation options.

## Requirements

- Python 3.13+
- [uv](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/) (for development & testing)

## Installation

```bash
pip install exec-python 
```

## Running the tests

```bash
uv run test_engine.py
```
